HEADWORD: Norther
<hw>North"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A wind from the
north; esp., a strong and cold north wind in Texas and the vicinity of
the Gulf of Mexico.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

